Document: AudioStreamGenerator
Path: godot/classes/class_audiostreamgenerator.rst
Summary: Defines properties for configuring the AudioStreamGenerator, including buffer length, mix rate, and mix rate mode.

Properties
* buffer_length (float): The length of the buffer in seconds. Default: 0.5
* mix_rate (float): The mix rate of the audio in Hz. Default: 44100.0
* mix_rate_mode (AudioStreamGeneratorMixRate): The mode for the mix rate. Default: 2
